1. install docker
	sudo apt-get install -y docker.io


2. check docker version
	docker --version

3.  install docker image / download centos from docker hub
	sudo docker pull centos:latest

4. to see docker images
	sudo docker images

5. To start CentOS, we need to issue a command to the OS to get a thread started
	sudo docker run -it centos /bin/bash


6. 
